import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IWorksheet } from '../worksheet.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-worksheet-detail', templateUrl: './worksheet-detail.component.html', }) export class WorksheetDetailComponent implements OnInit { worksheet: IWorksheet | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ worksheet }) => { this.worksheet = worksheet; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
